node.text:
Three takeaways:
1. Fran is *never* “Friendly” 🤪
2. Run through the finish line before you sprawl out on the floor.
3. No matter how well you executed a workout, you’re always going to say you think you could’ve gone faster 🙃 That’s why we love CrossFit am I right- always improvements to be made 😈
•••
🎥: @jtwiseguy

node.title: CrossFit Games Stage 1 Event 1- Friendly Fran

node.title: BEHIND THE HORNS EPISODE OF: GARAGE TRAINING SESSION WITH BROOKE WELLS

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Brooke Wells on July 23, 2021 tagging @compexusa, and @victakesashot. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text:
recovery is always extremely important in order for me to train at my full potential every single day. but it’s *especially* important right now considering we are 5(!!!) days out from the Games & I need my body ready to full send 😤🙌🏼 you won’t see me relaxing without my @compexusa 🙏🏼💁🏻‍♀️ let it do the recovery work for you!
#compex #compexusa #compexathlete
